3 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z"></path><path d="M20 3v4"></path><path d="M22 5h-4"></path><path d="M4 17v2"></path><path d="M5 18H3"></path></svg>Agence web bienveillante à Sète</div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(0px) translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground leading-tight">De l&#x27;idée au <span class="text-primary">premier client</span> en 3 semaines</h1></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">Sans jargon. Sans peur. Sans dépenser trop.<br class="hidden sm:block"/>On vous accompagne de A à Z pour lancer votre activité en ligne.</p></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center"><a href="#pricing" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium transition-all duration-fast focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background active:scale-[0.98] disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:w-4 [&amp;_svg]:h-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-sm hover:bg-primary/90 hover:shadow-md h-11 rounded-lg text-base px-8">Découvrir les offres<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 ml-2"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a><a href="#booking" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium transition-all duration-fast focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background active:scale-[0.98] disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:w-4 [&amp;_svg]:h-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-input bg-background shadow-sm hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground hover:border-accent hover:shadow-sm h-11 rounded-lg text-base px-8">Diagnostic gratuit</a></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><p class="mt-8 text-sm text-muted-foreground">À partir de <span class="font-semibold text-foreground">390€ HT</span> · Paiement en 4 fois possible</p></div></div></div></section><section id="problem" class="py-16 sm:py-24 scroll-mt-28 bg-secondary/30"><div class="mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-6xl"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14"><h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground">Vous avez l&#x27;idée. Vous avez <span class="text-primary">peur</span>.</h2><p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">Ces pensées vous empêchent de vous lancer ? On les connaît par cœur. Et on a des réponses.</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow h-full"><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-alert w-5 h-5 text-primary"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="8" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" x2="12.01" y1="16" y2="16"></line></svg></div><div><h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">&quot;C&#x27;est trop technique pour moi&quot;</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Vous n&#x27;avez pas besoin de savoir coder. On s&#x27;occupe de tout, vous vous occupez de votre métier.</p></div></div></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow h-full"><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-ban w-5 h-5 text-primary"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="m4.9 4.9 14.2 14.2"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">&quot;Je ne peux pas me permettre une agence web&quot;</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Nos tarifs commencent à 390€. Pas de surprises, pas de coûts cachés. Le prix affiché est le prix payé.</p></div></div></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow h-full"><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clock w-5 h-5 text-primary"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline></svg></div><div><h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">&quot;Je n&#x27;ai pas le temps d&#x27;apprendre&quot;</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">On vous forme en 45 minutes. Juste l&#x27;essentiel, en langage simple. Vous serez autonome, promis.</p></div></div></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow h-full"><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-help w-5 h-5 text-primary"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"></path><path d="M12 17h.01"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">&quot;Et si ça ne marche pas ?&quot;</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">On commence petit pour tester. Si l&#x27;idée fonctionne, on accélère ensemble. Zéro risque.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="solution" class="py-16 sm:py-24 scroll-mt-28"><div class="mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-6xl"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14"><h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground">Déclic lève toutes ces <span class="text-primary">barrières</span></h2><p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">Notre mission : rendre le web accessible à tous ceux qui ont une idée et l&#x27;envie de la concrétiser.</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all text-center h-full"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-heart w-6 h-6 text-primary"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Support humain</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Pas de chatbots, pas de répondeurs. Une vraie personne qui vous connaît et vous accompagne.</p></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all text-center h-full"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-eye w-6 h-6 text-primary"><path d="M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Tarifs transparents</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Le prix affiché est le prix final. Pas de frais cachés, pas de mauvaises surprises à la facturation.</p></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all text-center h-full"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-message-square w-6 h-6 text-primary"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Langage simple</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">On parle français, pas &quot;tech&quot;. Vous comprendrez chaque étape sans avoir besoin d&#x27;un dictionnaire.</p></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all text-center h-full"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-target w-6 h-6 text-primary"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Focus résultats</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">On ne compte pas les fonctionnalités : on compte vos clients. Votre succès est notre métrique.</p></div></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="mt-12 bg-accent/50 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center"><p class="text-foreground italic leading-relaxed">&quot;J&#x27;avais peur de me lancer. L&#x27;équipe Déclic m&#x27;a pris par la main, et en 3 semaines j&#x27;avais mes premiers clients. Simple, humain, efficace.&quot;</p><p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary">— Marie D., fleuriste à Sète</p></div></div></div></section><section id="process" class="py-16 sm:py-24 scroll-mt-28 bg-secondary/30"><div class="mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-6xl"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14"><h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground">3 semaines. 3 étapes. <span class="text-primary">Vos premiers clients.</span></h2><p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">Un processus simple et transparent, conçu pour vous faire gagner du temps et de la confiance.</p></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(0px) translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><div class="relative bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow h-full"><div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 -right-4 w-8 h-0.5 bg-primary/30"></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center text-primary-foreground font-bold text-sm">1</div><span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">Semaine 1</span></div><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-lightbulb w-5 h-5 text-primary"><path d="M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5"></path><path d="M9 18h6"></path><path d="M10 22h4"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">L&#x27;Idée</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">On discute de votre projet, on valide l&#x27;idée ensemble et on crée un plan clair. Pas de jargon, juste de la clarté.</p><ul class="space-y-1.5"><li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></div>Discussion et compréhension</li><li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></div>Validation du concept</li><li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></div>Plan d&#x27;action clair</li></ul></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(0px) translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><div class="relative bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow h-full"><div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 -right-4 w-8 h-0.5 bg-primary/30"></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center text-primary-foreground font-bold text-sm">2</div><span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">Semaine 2</span></div><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-code-xml w-5 h-5 text-primary"><path d="m18 16 4-4-4-4"></path><path d="m6 8-4 4 4 4"></path><path d="m14.5 4-5 16"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Le Site</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">On construit votre site, on intègre les outils essentiels et on vous forme en 45 minutes.</p><ul class="space-y-1.5"><li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></div>Construction du site</li><li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></div>Intégration des outils</li><li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></div>Formation 45 min</li></ul></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(0px) translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><div class="relative bg-card rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow h-full"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary flex items-center justify-center text-primary-foreground font-bold text-sm">3</div><span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">Semaine 3</span></div><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-rocket w-5 h-5 text-primary"><path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z"></path><path d="m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z"></path><path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0"></path><path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Les Clients</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">On lance ensemble, on ajuste si besoin et on vous accompagne pour vos premiers clients.</p><ul class="space-y-1.5"><li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></div>Mise en ligne</li><li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></div>Ajustements</li><li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary flex-shrink-0"></div>Accompagnement clients</li></ul></div></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="mt-12 text-center"><a href="#booking" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium transition-all duration-fast focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background active:scale-[0.98] disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:w-4 [&amp;_svg]:h-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-sm hover:bg-primary/90 hover:shadow-md h-11 rounded-lg px-6 text-base">Voyons ensemble</a></div></div></div></section><section id="pricing" class="py-16 sm:py-24 scroll-mt-28"><div class="mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-6xl"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6"><h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground">Des offres honnêtes pour <span class="text-primary">tous les budgets</span></h2><p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">Pas de coûts cachés. Pas de mauvaises surprises. Juste des prix justes pour un travail de qualité.</p></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="flex justify-center mb-10"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-secondary rounded-full p-1"><button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-all bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-sm">Paiement unique</button><button class="px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-all text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground">En 4 fois</button></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 items-stretch"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="relative bg-card rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all h-full flex flex-col "><div class="mb-6"><h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Pack Essai</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1">Tester une idée sans risque</p></div><div class="mb-6"><div class="flex items-baseline gap-1"><span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">390€</span><span class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">HT</span></div></div><ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1"><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Landing page standalone</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Design responsive moderne</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">1 mois de maintenance gratuite</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Mise en ligne en 1 semaine</span></li></ul><a href="#booking" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-fast focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background active:scale-[0.98] disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:w-4 [&amp;_svg]:h-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-input bg-background shadow-sm hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground hover:border-accent hover:shadow-sm h-10 px-4 py-2 w-full">Choisir cette offre<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 ml-2"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="relative bg-card rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all h-full flex flex-col ring-2 ring-primary shadow-md"><div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent hover:bg-primary/80 absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-star w-3 h-3 mr-1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon></svg> Recommandé</div><div class="mb-6"><h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Pack Déclic</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1">Lancement officiel + premiers clients</p></div><div class="mb-6"><div class="flex items-baseline gap-1"><span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">890€</span><span class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">HT</span></div></div><ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1"><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Site complet 5 pages</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Intégration Google Maps</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Bouton WhatsApp</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Formation 45 min (utilisation + bases)</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Système de réservation (sync Google Calendar)</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Formulaire de contact + notifications</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">3 mois de maintenance gratuite</span></li></ul><a href="#booking" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-fast focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background active:scale-[0.98] disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:w-4 [&amp;_svg]:h-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-sm hover:bg-primary/90 hover:shadow-md h-10 px-4 py-2 w-full">Choisir cette offre<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 ml-2"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="relative bg-card rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all h-full flex flex-col "><div class="mb-6"><h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Pack Accélérateur</h3><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1">Scale avec confiance + positionnement premium</p></div><div class="mb-6"><div class="flex items-baseline gap-1"><span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">1690€</span><span class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">HT</span></div></div><ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1"><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Tout du Pack Déclic +</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Coaching 1-to-1 (stratégie 10 premiers clients)</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Service de copywriting (pages, emails)</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Design logo simple</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">Blog pour content marketing</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check w-4 h-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="text-foreground">6 mois de maintenance gratuite</span></li></ul><a href="#booking" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-fast focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background active:scale-[0.98] disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:w-4 [&amp;_svg]:h-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-input bg-background shadow-sm hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground hover:border-accent hover:shadow-sm h-10 px-4 py-2 w-full">Choisir cette offre<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 ml-2"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><p class="text-center mt-8 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Sans risque. Satisfaction garantie. Maintenance à partir de 29€/mois après la période gratuite.</p></div></div></section><section class="py-16 sm:py-24 scroll-mt-28 bg-secondary/30"><div class="mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-6xl"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14"><h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground">Pourquoi nous faire <span class="text-primary">confiance</span> ?</h2></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-center h-full"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-credit-card w-5 h-5 text-primary"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="5" rx="2"></rect><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="10" y2="10"></line></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Paiement flexible</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs leading-relaxed">Payez en 4 fois sans frais sur les packs Déclic et Accélérateur.</p></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-center h-full"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield w-5 h-5 text-primary"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Garantie sans jargon</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs leading-relaxed">Si vous ne comprenez pas quelque chose, on vous l&#x27;explique autrement. Toujours.</p></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-center h-full"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-user-check w-5 h-5 text-primary"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><polyline points="16 11 18 13 22 9"></polyline></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Support personnel</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs leading-relaxed">Un interlocuteur dédié, pas un robot. Vous méritez une vraie personne.</p></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-center h-full"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5 text-primary"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Résultats rapides</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs leading-relaxed">Vos premiers clients en quelques semaines, pas en quelques mois.</p></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px) translateZ(0)"><div class="bg-card rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-center h-full"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up w-5 h-5 text-primary"><path d="M7 10v12"></path><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Satisfait ou remboursé</h3><p class="text-muted-foreground text-xs leading-relaxed">Si le résultat ne vous plaît pas, on travaille jusqu&#x27;a votre satisfaction.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id="faq" class="py-16 sm:py-24 scroll-mt-28"><div class="mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="text-center mb-12"><div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-help w-6 h-6 text-primary"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"></path><path d="M12 17h.01"></path></svg></div><h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground">Vos questions, nos <span class="text-primary">réponses honnêtes</span></h2></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px) translateZ(0)"><div class="w-full" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b border-border/50"><h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-:R8qesuqj6:" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-:Rqesuqj6:" class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between transition-all [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180 text-left font-medium text-foreground hover:no-underline hover:text-primary py-5 text-base" data-radix-collection-item="">Je n&#x27;y connais rien en web, c&#x27;est grave ?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state="closed" id="radix-:R8qesuqj6:" hidden="" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-:Rqesuqj6:" data-orientation="vertical" class="overflow-hidden text-sm transition-all data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up data-[state=open]:animate-accordion-down" style="--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)"></div></div><div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b border-border/50"><h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-:R9aesuqj6:" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-:R1aesuqj6:" class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between transition-all [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180 text-left font-medium text-foreground hover:no-underline hover:text-primary py-5 text-base" data-radix-collection-item="">C&#x27;est trop cher pour moi, non ?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state="closed" id="radix-:R9aesuqj6:" hidden="" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-:R1aesuqj6:" data-orientation="vertical" class="overflow-hidden text-sm transition-all data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up data-[state=open]:animate-accordion-down" style="--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)"></div></div><div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b border-border/50"><h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-:R9qesuqj6:" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-:R1qesuqj6:" class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between transition-all [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180 text-left font-medium text-foreground hover:no-underline hover:text-primary py-5 text-base" data-radix-collection-item="">Combien de temps ça prend ?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state="closed" id="radix-:R9qesuqj6:" hidden="" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-:R1qesuqj6:" data-orientation="vertical" class="overflow-hidden text-sm transition-all data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up data-[state=open]:animate-accordion-down" style="--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)"></div></div><div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b border-border/50"><h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-:Raaesuqj6:" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-:R2aesuqj6:" class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between transition-all [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180 text-left font-medium text-foreground hover:no-underline hover:text-primary py-5 text-base" data-radix-collection-item="">Et si mon idée ne marche pas ?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state="closed" id="radix-:Raaesuqj6:" hidden="" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-:R2aesuqj6:" data-orientation="vertical" class="overflow-hidden text-sm transition-all data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up data-[state=open]:animate-accordion-down" style="--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)"></div></div><div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b border-border/50"><h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-:Raqesuqj6:" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-:R2qesuqj6:" class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between transition-all [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180 text-left font-medium text-foreground hover:no-underline hover:text-primary py-5 text-base" data-radix-collection-item="">Combien ça coûte vraiment, au total ?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state="closed" id="radix-:Raqesuqj6:" hidden="" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-:R2qesuqj6:" data-orientation="vertical" class="overflow-hidden text-sm transition-all data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up data-[state=open]:animate-accordion-down" style="--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)"></div></div><div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b border-border/50"><h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-:Rbaesuqj6:" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-:R3aesuqj6:" class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between transition-all [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180 text-left font-medium text-foreground hover:no-underline hover:text-primary py-5 text-base" data-radix-collection-item="">Je n&#x27;ai vraiment pas le temps, comment ça se passe ?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state="closed" id="radix-:Rbaesuqj6:" hidden="" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-:R3aesuqj6:" data-orientation="vertical" class="overflow-hidden text-sm transition-all data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up data-[state=open]:animate-accordion-down" style="--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)"></div></div><div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b border-border/50"><h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-:Rbqesuqj6:" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-:R3qesuqj6:" class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between transition-all [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180 text-left font-medium text-foreground hover:no-underline hover:text-primary py-5 text-base" data-radix-collection-item="">Qu&#x27;est-ce qui est inclus dans la maintenance ?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state="closed" id="radix-:Rbqesuqj6:" hidden="" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-:R3qesuqj6:" data-orientation="vertical" class="overflow-hidden text-sm transition-all data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up data-[state=open]:animate-accordion-down" style="--radix-accordion-content-height:var(--radix-collapsible-content-height);--radix-accordion-content-width:var(--radix-collapsible-content-width)"></div></div><div data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" class="border-b border-border/50"><h3 data-orientation="vertical" data-state="closed" class="flex"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-:Rcaesuqj6:" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical" id="radix-:R4aesuqj6:" class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-between transition-all [&amp;[data-state=open]&gt;svg]:rotate-180 text-left font-medium text-foreground hover:no-underline hover:text-primary py-5 text-base" data-radix-collection-item="">Je peux modifier mon site moi-même après ?<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></h3><div data-state="closed" id="radix-:Rcaesuqj6:" hidden="" role="region" aria-labelledby="radix-:R4aesuqj6:" data-orientation="vertical" class="overflow-hidden text-sm transition-all data-[state=closed]:animate-accordion-up da